Present trial is the third study that in combination with two completed studies (one being a trial in hepatic resection surgery also comparing TachoSil(R) and Surgicel(R) Original) targeted toward providing clinical safety and efficacy data to support extending the current label of TachoSil(R) to a general hemostasis indication across several surgical procedures and organ systems in the USA.

